            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I was a student of this school and I am heartbroken to say this was not the experience I had imagined to have as being goenkan.Firstly I would like to say about the physical fitness, there was this sir who made agirl feel uncomfortable around him. Secondly, about the education there is this one teacher who took many holidays and did not come to school then afternoon she came she forgot to complete the syllabus of half yearly.\nWhen half yearly were around the corner she said to the students to complete the syllabus ourselves which was really difficult at the time.When parents told the principal about some serious issues no serious action was taken instead they spread rumors about that parent.If some senior students bullied some juniors then that student would not be expelled instead they would just give a warning or do not even give a glance to it or worst case scenario they would just suspend them for 2-3 days and that student would again start coming to school normally",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
