            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "GD Goenka School is doing excellent in all the fields especially giving a lot of exposure to children.I am very grateful to Management,  Principal Ma'am, teachers and whole staff, also a very special thanks to Deepali Ma'am and Shahida  Ma'am .A special mention to Sushma Ma'am and Shweta Ma'am who were great pillars of strength for my child. Keep it up! I wish a great success to GD Goenka Global School.\n\nHowever,  I would like to mention that although extra curricular activities are a must, there should be more serious studies and practice for the board examinations for 10th and 12th standard.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
