            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Even this phrase \"NAAM BADE AUR DARSHAN CHOTE\" is not suitable for this school.\nThis is not a school. It is just a Business for them.\nLoot hard earned money from the parents.\nConstruction is happening that's why they start Summer break early and start late. What a pathetical excuse they are providing (heat condition). Are their classrooms are under Tamboo.\nAfter few days they will make excuse its heavy rain, lets have a break. Looks we are giving fees for breaks only.\nYou pick any book of last session. Half of the chapters were untouched due to their lack of planning.\nThey never compensate any Saturday or Sunday if any unwanted holiday occurs.\nInstead of on-going construction just shut-down it. That will be much better for all.",
